data.description: Room to roam in Canton South! This fantastic 4 BR, 3.5 bath home is a total of 3,004 sq ft with a finished walk out in lower level. From the spacious front porch, the large dining room to the massive open kitchen and great room, there is enough room for everyone. Huge 2nd floor master with large soaking tub, double sinks and a walk closet. 3 more large bedrooms round out the 2nd floor.  The walk out lower level has a wet bar , full bath with walk in shower and a pool table that stays.   Outside is truly tranquil and park like with patio and deck   Tucked away in a wooded allotment with brand new school just minutes away and is conveniently located close to major highways.
